<h1>Pay Online</h1>
<p>If you would like to make a tuition or other payment online, we will allow you to do so through Paypal. However, please be aware that the fee that is charged by Paypal comes out of the amount you pay before being applied to your account. Please add on 3% to your payments. For example, if you want to make a payment of $100 on your account, please pay $103.00. The amount we receive after the fee will be applied directly to your account.</p>
<p><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220518103148/https://www.paypal.me/TheEinsteinAcademy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Click here to make a payment</a></p>
</div></div>
